  <lyrics>[V1]
 Diosan arupajj saraquistuwa. janiy llaquisipjjamtejja
 Mank'an toketsa, uxnafi umatsa, janchin isipatsa.
 
[C] 
 Nayrakatajja thaktapjjañániy
 Diosan alajjpach marcapa;
 Ucqharojj Diosajj take cunracwa
 Churaraquistani.
 
[V2]
 Uñtapjjainaya jarnach'inaca, janiw yapuchapquitejja,
 Alajjpach suma Awquisaquiwa mank'afi churaraqui.
 
[V3]
 Uñtapjjarnaya pankaranacsa, ucqha sum isthapisipjje
 Janiw kapupquis, janiw sawupquis, Diosaw isthapiyi.
 
[V4]
 Jamach'it sipan, pankarat sipan, amparan cayunitanwa.
 Diosaraquiwa bendicistani irnakáwisaru.
 
</lyrics></song>